", "original": "After their first meeting, Maximus offered to show Luna around Catville.
“Would you like me to give you a tour of the city?” he asked politely.

“That would be wonderful,” she replied.

“You seem very popular here,” she said with a playful grin.

Maximus chuckled.
“Not really. I just try to help whenever I can. If someone is in trouble, I can’t ignore it.”

“Thank you, Maximus. I think Catville feels a little more like home now.”
